            <title>[FELIX-2276] Authentication credentials for proxies are not set when retrieving resources</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/FELIX-2276</link>
                <project id="12310100" key="FELIX">Felix</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;OBR sets authentication credentials when retrieving the repository.xml file, but not when retrieving resources. Thus, while it is possible to see what&apos;s available from behind a proxy, it&apos;s not possible to actually deploy anything.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
