                            <comment id="12856451" author="gnt" created="Tue, 13 Apr 2010 15:30:44 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I&apos;ve fixed the issue. &lt;br/&gt;
However, I wonder why we don&apos;t expect the user to use the java.net.Authenticator class which seems to fulfil this exact purpose.&lt;br/&gt;
Note that the java.net.Authenticator is a system wide singleton, so I don&apos;t really think OBR should configure it, but the felix / karaf launcher could set up one and we could remove that code from bundlerepository.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Thoughts anyone ?&lt;/p&gt;

